
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <!-- Standard Meta -->
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0">

  <!-- Site Properties -->
  <title>Homepage - Linguanski</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/styles/semantic.css">

  <style type="text/css">

    .hidden.menu {
      display: none;
    }

    .masthead.segment {
      min-height: 600px;
      padding: 1em 0em;
    }
    .masthead .logo.item img {
      margin-right: 1em;
    }
    .masthead .ui.menu .ui.button {
      margin-left: 0.5em;
    }
    .masthead h1.ui.header {
      margin-top: 3em;
      margin-bottom: 0em;
      font-size: 4em;
      font-weight: normal;
    }
    .masthead h2 {
      font-size: 1.7em;
      font-weight: normal;
    }

    .ui.vertical.stripe {
      padding: 8em 0em;
    }
    .ui.vertical.stripe h3 {
      font-size: 2em;
    }
    .ui.vertical.stripe .button + h3,
    .ui.vertical.stripe p + h3 {
      margin-top: 3em;
    }
    .ui.vertical.stripe .floated.image {
      clear: both;
    }
    .ui.vertical.stripe p {
      font-size: 1.33em;
    }
    .ui.vertical.stripe .horizontal.divider {
      margin: 3em 0em;
    }

    .quote.stripe.segment {
      padding: 0em;
    }
    .quote.stripe.segment .grid .column {
      padding-top: 5em;
      padding-bottom: 5em;
    }

    .footer.segment {
      padding: 5em 0em;
    }

    .secondary.pointing.menu .toc.item {
      display: none;
    }

    @media only screen and (max-width: 700px) {
      .ui.fixed.menu {
        display: none !important;
      }
      .secondary.pointing.menu .item,
      .secondary.pointing.menu .menu {
        display: none;
      }
      .secondary.pointing.menu .toc.item {
        display: block;
      }
      .masthead.segment {
        min-height: 350px;
      }
      .masthead h1.ui.header {
        font-size: 2em;
        margin-top: 1.5em;
      }
      .masthead h2 {
        margin-top: 0.5em;
        font-size: 1.5em;
      }
    }
    .ui.inverted.segment, .ui.primary.inverted.segment {
      background-image: url(/images/paisajes-naturales-descargar-wallpapers-wallpaper.jpg);
      /*background-image: url(/images/2693.jpg);*/
      /*background-image: url(https://image.freepik.com/foto-gratis/habitacion-difuminada-con-ventanas_1048-2669.jpg);*/
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-size: cover;
      -webkit-background-size: cover;
      -moz-background-size: cover;
      -o-background-size: cover;
    }

  </style>

  <script src="/js/dependencies/jquery-3.1.1.js"></script>

  <script>
  $(document)
    .ready(function() {

      // fix menu when passed
      $('.masthead')
        .visibility({
          once: false,
          onBottomPassed: function() {
            $('.fixed.menu').transition('fade in');
          },
          onBottomPassedReverse: function() {
            $('.fixed.menu').transition('fade out');
          }
        })
      ;

      // create sidebar and attach to menu open
      $('.ui.sidebar')
        .sidebar('attach events', '.toc.item')
      ;

    })
  ;
  </script>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Following Menu -->
<div class="ui large top fixed hidden menu">
  <div class="ui container">
    <a class="active item">LINGUANSKI</a>
    <div class="right menu">
      <div class="item">
        <a class="ui button" href="/account/signin"><%= __('Login') %></a>
      </div>
      <div class="item">
        <a class="ui primary button" href="/account/signup"><%= __('Sign Up') %></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Sidebar Menu -->
<div class="ui vertical inverted sidebar menu">
  <a class="active item">LINGUANSKI</a>
  <a class="item" href="/account/signin"><%= __('Login') %></a>
  <a class="item" href="/account/signup"><%= __('Sign Up') %></a>
</div>


<!-- Page Contents -->
<div class="pusher">
  <div class="ui inverted vertical masthead center aligned segment">

    <div class="ui container">
      <div class="ui large secondary inverted pointing menu">
        <a class="toc item">
          <i class="sidebar icon"></i>
        </a>
        <a class="active item">LINGUANSKI</a>
        <div class="right item">
          <% if(req.session.authenticated){ %>
            <a class="ui inverted button" href="/dashboard"><%= __('Dashboard') %></a>
          <% }else{ %>
            <a class="ui inverted button" href="/account/signin"><%= __('Login') %></a>
            <a class="ui inverted button" href="/account/signup"><%= __('Sign Up') %></a>
          <% } %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ui text container">
      <% if(req.session.authenticated){ %>
        <h1 class="ui inverted header">
          <%= __('Welcome') %> <%= req.session.user.name %>
        </h1>
        <h2>Siga practicando.</h2>
        <a href="/dashboard" class="ui huge primary button"> <%= __('Ir a dashboard') %> <i class="right arrow icon"></i></a>
      <% }else{ %>
      <h1 class="ui inverted header">
        Linguanski
      </h1>
      <h2><%= __('Practise a language with phrases.') %></h2>
      <a href="/account/signin" class="ui huge primary button"> <%= __('Sign Up') %> <i class="right arrow icon"></i></a>
      <% } %>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="ui vertical stripe segment">
    <div class="ui middle aligned stackable grid container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="eight wide column">
          <h3 class="ui header"><%= __('Understand a language') %></h3>
          <p>Impulsamos su conocimiento en la escritura con dinamicas que le ayudaran en el aprendizaje de su idioma favorito.</p>
          <h3 class="ui header">Aprenda a su propio ritmo</h3>
          <p>Solo necesita registrarse y un asistente le ayudara a elegir las frases personalizadas.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="six wide right floated column">
          <!-- <img src="/images/characters-interface-sign.png" class="ui large bordered rounded image"> -->
          <img src="https://thumb9.shutterstock.com/display_pic_with_logo/11994/614722418/stock-vector-hello-hand-drawn-word-cloud-in-different-languages-of-the-world-background-concept-614722418.jpg" class="ui large bordered rounded image">
          <div>Icons made by <a href="http://www.freepik.com" title="Freepik">Freepik</a> from <a href="http://www.flaticon.com" title="Flaticon">www.flaticon.com</a> is licensed by <a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/" title="Creative Commons BY 3.0" target="_blank">CC 3.0 BY</a></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="center aligned column">
          <a class="ui huge button" href="/account/signin"><%= __('Login') %></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>


  <div class="ui vertical stripe quote segment">
    <div class="ui equal width stackable internally celled grid">
      <div class="center aligned row">
        <div class="column">
          <h3>"Aprender con ellos es verdaderamente sencillo."</h3>
          <p>@usuariofan1</p>
        </div>
        <div class="column">
          <h3>"Me preocupe por la escritura del idioma ruso y ahí surgió la idea."</h3>
          <p>
            <img src="https://blog.alexandermiss.com/content/images/2017/01/zbFAdw_G_400x400.jpg" class="ui avatar image"> <b>@AlexanderMiss</b> CEO de Linguanski
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="ui vertical stripe segment">
    <div class="ui text container">
      <h3 class="ui header">Nos preocupamos por el aprendizaje</h3>
      <p>Cada dinámica está construída por nuestros expertos que te ayudarán a entiender de la mejor manera posible.</p>
      <a class="ui large button"><%= __('Read More') %></a>
      <h4 class="ui horizontal header divider">
        <a href="/account/signup"><%= __('Case Studies') %></a>
      </h4>
      <h3 class="ui header">Seguimos trabajando en mejoras</h3>
      <p>Para construir un mejor aprendizaje renovamos nuestras dinámicas para hacerte sentir a gusto.</p>
      <a class="ui large button" href="/account/signup">Sí, quiero registrarme</a>
    </div>
  </div>


  <div class="ui inverted vertical footer segment">
    <div class="ui container">
      <div class="ui stackable inverted divided equal height stackable grid">
        <div class="three wide column">
          <h4 class="ui inverted header">About</h4>
          <div class="ui inverted link list">
            <a href="#" class="item">FAQ</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="three wide column">
          <h4 class="ui inverted header">Services</h4>
          <div class="ui inverted link list">
            <a href="#" class="item">About us</a>
            <a href="#" class="item">Contact Us</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="seven wide column">
          <h4 class="ui inverted header">Diviértete</h4>
          <p>Juega con las frases en otros idiomas y te divertirás aprendiendo.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

</body>

</html>
